| âœ… | **Advanced Models**                   | Supports large models like **LLaMA 3.1 70B** via the Groq API.               |
| âœ… | **Automated QA Generation**         | Generate question-answer pairs from input text.                             |
| âœ… | **Hugging Face Datasets**    | Convert QA pairs to Hugging Face datasets, then export or upload datasets to Hugging Face. |
| âœ… | **Custom Split Ratios**              | Define custom train/test split ratios when generating QA pairs. |
| âœ… | **Prompt Templates**                | Flexible question generation through prompt templates.                      |
| âœ… | **Customizable Configurations**     | Configure via CLI, `config.json`, or directly in Python code.                              |

